						<h3>Payroll Processing</h3>
						<p>We calculate and process payroll, including salary payments, tax deductions, and employer contributions (CPP, EI, QPP, QPIP).</p>
					</div>
					<div class="handle-card">
						<h3>Tax Compliance</h3>
						<p>We remit all required taxes to the CRA, generate T4/T4A tax slips, and ensure full compliance with Canadian tax requirements.</p>
					</div>
