						<h3>Record Keeping</h3>
						<p>We maintain all employment records, time tracking, ROE generation, and documentation required by Canadian law.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="benefits section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Benefits of the EOR Model</h2>
					<p>Why U.S. companies choose the EOR approach</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefits-list">
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>No Entity Formation Required</h3>
						<p>Skip the complexity and cost of forming a Canadian corporation. No need to register with the CRA, open payroll accounts, or set up provincial compliance.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Fast Onboarding</h3>
						<p>Hire Canadian talent in 24-48 hours instead of waiting 3-6 months for entity formation and setup. Get your team working quickly.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Full Compliance</h3>
						<p>We ensure complete compliance with all Canadian employment laws, tax requirements, and regulatory obligations. No compliance risks for you.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Cost Effective</h3>
						<p>Avoid the upfront costs of entity formation ($5,000-$15,000+) and ongoing compliance management. One simple monthly fee covers everything.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Scalable</h3>
						<p>Easily scale up or down as your needs change. Add or remove employees without the complexity of managing a Canadian entity.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Transparent Billing</h3>
						<p>One monthly invoice with no hidden fees. You know exactly what you're paying for: salary + employer contributions + service fee.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

