					<p>Learn more about our Employer of Record services and how we can help you hire Canadian talent quickly, legally, and cost-effectively.</p>
					<a href="/eor" class="btn btn-primary">Learn About EOR Services</a>
					<p class="cta-email">Or email us at <a href="mailto:marc@infradevconsulting.com">marc@infradevconsulting.com</a></p>
				</div>
